title: Fable Lore
description: Fable Lore is a unique modlist that takes on the deleveling aspect of Skyrim modding to a whole new experience, where instead of relying on an already existing mod, such as Requiem, and building the list around it, the deleveled experience is built around the list. Utilizing Synthesis, the modlist comes with a completely custom add-on built specifically for the list that delevels the entire world, as well as hundreds of thousands of tweaks and balancing to account for every single mod in the list.
author: Rage

title: Wasteland Prospects
description: Explore Nevada all over again, with a new and invigorating look on the Wasteland. Explore new areas, meet new friends, take on challenging enemies, and see what New Vegas is all about. Featured as just a New Vegas modlist, you won't be restricted to a complex setup with TTW, but instead focus your travels on Nevada. Take on a new look of New Vegas, with an ever growing list of graphical adjustments and improvements. Experience classic weapons with completely fresh and new animations and discover new weapons and equipment.
author: Rage
